    <item>
      <title>莫迪呼吁废除印度宗教法律</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/modi-calls-for-an-end-to-india-s-religion-based-laws</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度总理纳伦德拉·莫迪再次呼吁以统一的民法典取代印度的宗教法，但此举遭到一些少数群体的反对。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/modi-calls-for-an-end-to-india-s-religion-based-laws</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 06:29:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>服务业助力英国经济保持强劲复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/uk-economy-maintains-solid-recovery-in-fillip-for-keir-starmer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国经济从去年的经济衰退中保持了稳步复苏的步伐，为首相基尔·斯塔默寻求促进经济增长和修复公共财政提供了强大的经济基础。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/uk-economy-maintains-solid-recovery-in-fillip-for-keir-starmer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 06:09:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯将提议禁止食品和杂货“哄抬价格”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/harris-will-propose-price-gouging-ban-on-food-and-groceries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国副总统卡马拉·哈里斯的竞选团队在她即将举行的总统竞选的首次政策演讲预告中表示，她将呼吁联邦政府禁止食品和杂货价格欺诈，这是旨在降低消费者成本的一系列更广泛提案的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/harris-will-propose-price-gouging-ban-on-food-and-groceries</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 04:27:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国总统尹永康向金正恩抛出罕见橄榄枝</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/south-korea-s-yoon-offers-rare-olive-branch-to-kim-jong-un</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈向朝鲜提出援助、对话和统一道路，以此向这个曾辱骂他并威胁要消灭其首尔政府的邻国做出新的接触。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/south-korea-s-yoon-offers-rare-olive-branch-to-kim-jong-un</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 02:46:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>他信盟友成为泰国领导人的领跑者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/thaksin-loyalist-emerges-pm-frontrunner-as-parties-begin-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国议会将于星期五举行会议选举新领导人，在此之前，泰国各政党将进行会谈，就由长期效忠他信·西那瓦的人担任下一任总理达成共识。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/thaksin-loyalist-emerges-pm-frontrunner-as-parties-begin-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 02:43:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新泽西州州长墨菲将任命前助理接替梅内德斯</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/new-jersey-s-murphy-to-appoint-former-aide-to-replace-menendez</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士周三晚间透露，新泽西州州长菲尔墨菲将任命其前幕僚长接替上个月因联邦腐败指控被定罪的参议员鲍勃梅嫩德斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/new-jersey-s-murphy-to-appoint-former-aide-to-replace-menendez</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 02:42:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡下一任总统竞选的关键候选人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/the-key-contenders-in-race-to-become-sri-lanka-s-next-president</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡下个月举行的总统选举正成为政治精英与曾因武装叛乱而臭名昭著的左翼组织之间的战场，候选人争夺负责监督亟待改革的经济的最高职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/the-key-contenders-in-race-to-become-sri-lanka-s-next-president</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 15 Aug 2024 02:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>分析师称泰国市场面临政治风险压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-15/thai-markets-face-pressure-over-political-risk-street-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受泰国总理下台后政策实施可能推迟的担忧影响，泰国资产价格下跌。]]></description>
